A '''cluster grenade''' was a type of [[Grenade/Legends|grenade]] which was used by, among others, [[Renegade Squadron/Legends|Renegade Squadron]].

Once thrown, the cluster grenade multiplied damage potential by exploding a charge in midair and dropping four smaller charges in a several [[Meter/Legends|meter]] radius. The charges exploded upon impact with heavy damage within the radius of each.

